              "body": "Hi team,\n\nThe following is a summary of Sales Pipeline & Forecast for Q3. Changes from last week's figures are noted. All figures in CAD.\n\nNotable changes to opportunities in the past week are detailed below.\n\nClosed Won\n\nJust Energy - $45K MRC - Install Base, Hosting\n\n3 month contract for temporary licensing\n\nClosed Lost\n\nUS Signal - $27K MRC - New Logo, SaaS\n\nNational Relief Telecom - $20K MRC - New Logo, SaaS\n\nNewly Created\n\nJust Energy - $75K MRC - Install Base, Managed Services, Q4\n\nClose Date Pushed\n\nIguana Solutions - $12K MRC (New Logo, Hosting, pushed from Mar to Apr)\n\nAC Foods - $75K NRC (New Logo, PS, pushed from May to Jun)\n\nEBOARDsolutions - $33K NRC (Install Base, PS, pushed from Apr to Sep)\n\nMRC or NRC Changed\n\nNo notable changes\n\n***\n\nTo see performance against targets, opportunity details, or other sales analysis please refer to the Power BI Dashboards (updated daily):\n\nSales Forecasting & Analysis - Power BI Dashboards\n\nThanks,\n\nTom Kelsch\n\nSenior Decision Support Analyst\n\naptum.com | LinkedIn",
